%% End-to-end sequence: a tick becomes a rendered frame
sequenceDiagram
  participant S as Simulator
  participant K as Redpanda
  participant A as Aggregator
  participant G as Gateway
  participant W as Web (Zustand)
  participant R as React (rAF)

  S->>K: produce tick (market.ticks)
  S->>K: produce trades (market.trades)
  K->>A: consume tick + trades
  A->>A: build candles + stats (pure utils)
  A->>K: produce candle / metrics
  K->>G: consume all topics
  G->>G: route by channel index, coalesce per client
  G-->>W: batched frame (≈40Hz)
  W->>W: applyBatch (one store write)
  R->>W: read narrow selector on next frame
  R-->>R: paint changed cells only
